Text: I've been looking for IDW Transformers. Most everything before 2008 is already out there but not the series published since then. Need All Hail Megatron, some of Transformers Ongoing and the last couple mini-series.

I posted 1-16 of "All Hail Megatron" here: http://thepiratebay.se/torrent/7266741/The_Transformers_-_All_Hail_Megatron_01-16

I'll have to look for the others.

I signed up just to leave this comment- this is one of the better curated collections of comics that I have seen yet. As in "ever". Great job getting this collection together and organized as it is.

Thank you very much.

Thanks for your efforts. You wouldn't happen to have the Wynonna Earp books, would you? I have Yeti Wars physical books, but that and the other IDW Earp series would be awesome in digital. I have the Image series from the 90s in digital just not the IDW. Thanks!!
Oops. I just now noticed the set I was looking for, Home On the Strange, was listed in here. Hopefully it will still be seeded enough to get it.
